Class CustomCommandScope

java.lang.Object
org.forgerock.openidm.shell.CustomCommandScope
Direct Known Subclasses:
BasicCommandScope, LocalCommandScope, RemoteCommandScope
public abstract class CustomCommandScope extends Object
An abstract command scope for the Felix Gogo command processor.
